conversation_log.message: MOLECULAR VISION: Unleash a sonic barrage by slicing vowels, fracturing consonants, and interlacing fragments of both tracks into a chaotic tapestry. Inject synthetic formant shifts, granular delays, and phasic explosions for maximum dissonance. Create an auditory upheaval where natural vocal boundaries dissolve into a molecular storm that defies coherence — pure vocal entropy.
